    {
      "end": 135.67999267578125,
      "text": "And I don't want to repeat anything that you've done before.",
      "start": 129.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 138.13999938964844,
      "text": "I want to show you some more.",
      "start": 135.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 140.94000244140625,
      "text": "I want to love you.",
      "start": 138.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 144.94000244140625,
      "text": "Like you've never been found out before.",
      "start": 140.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 146.1999969482422,
      "text": "I'm rocked down again.",
      "start": 145.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 149.86000061035156,
      "text": "I'm talking about questions of eternity.",
      "start": 146.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 152.8800048828125,
      "text": "Conversation knocks your left out loud.",
      "start": 150.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 155.1199951171875,
      "text": "Knocks your breath out loud.",
      "start": 153.24000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 157.32000732421875,
      "text": "Makes you say out loud.",
      "start": 155.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 160.0800018310547,
      "text": "Makes you exclaim.",
      "start": 158.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 162.39999389648438,
      "text": "Tonight is our night.",
      "start": 160.5
    },
    {
      "end": 162.9600067138672,
      "text": "",
      "start": 162.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 166.8800048828125,
      "text": "Baby, when you come with me, you know we can be free.",
      "start": 163.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 170.13999938964844,
      "text": "We can float on ecstasy in the moon glow.",
      "start": 167
    },
    {
      "end": 171.47999572753906,
      "text": "Dancing in the moonlight.",
      "start": 170.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 173.25999450683594,
      "text": "Dancing in the moon, you know.",
      "start": 171.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 175.0399932861328,
      "text": "We can be there.",
      "start": 173.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 176.77999877929688,
      "text": "I don't even know what we do.",
      "start": 175.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 181.66000366210938,
      "text": "But for starters, maybe we talk all night and find something blue.",
      "start": 176.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 183.33999633789062,
      "text": "To be put in with.",
      "start": 182.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 184.5399932861328,
      "text": "To be more than that.",
      "start": 183.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 187.0800018310547,
      "text": "To have a little escape and be more than that.",
      "start": 184.5800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 189.25999450683594,
      "text": "Who knows what tomorrow brings?",
      "start": 187.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 193.5800018310547,
      "text": "But I know that you are the fire that ignites the night.",
      "start": 189.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 196.13999938964844,
      "text": "The fire that ignites the night.",
      "start": 193.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 197.66000366210938,
      "text": "I'm rooting for you.",
      "start": 196.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 199.1199951171875,
      "text": "I'm wishing for you, man.",
      "start": 197.8800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 256.1199951171875,
